snippet.title: The Survivalists Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Play alone, or in co-op online with up to three friends in our new survival game set in the Escapists Universe: The Survivalists.  

Explore, build and craft your way on Nintendo Switch, PS4, Xbox One and Steam in 2020.​

Game Page: https://www.team17.com/games/the-survivalists/
Follow The Survivalists on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SurvivalistsT17
Like The Survivalists on Facebook: https://facebook.com/SurvivalistsT17

Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Aven Colony, The Escapists, Genesis Alpha One, Overcooked, Sword Legacy: Omen, Yoku’s Island Express, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
